::Feline::

She wrapped her arms around him.  She purred lightly as he kissed 
her. She stood up and kept kissing him.  This was going to be a VERY 
pleasuable assignment.  She would have to thank Zardus properly when 
this was all over.
She pulled back and looked into his eyes. "Are you sure there isn't 
anyway I can repay you for you kindness?" she said in a soft and 
breathy voice. She kissed him and glided her hand down his back.  She 
took one claw and traced his spine. She whispered "If there is 
anything I can do...." she let her sentance trail off as she 
continued to kiss him.
